  "original_title": "\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bcb\u0ba4\u0ba9\u0bbe \u0bb5\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0b9a\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb0 \u0baa\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb0 \u0bb5\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bb4\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Provision of two-wheelers to Jaffna Teaching Hospital health workers",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "10 two-wheelers were handed over to Jaffna Teaching Hospital to facilitate the transportation of health workers.",
        "The fuel shortage in the country has also affected the transport of health workers and the prices of two-wheelers have also increased.",
        "To solve this crisis, British Car Welfare Association has donated ten double wheeled cars to the Jaffna Teaching Hospital.",
        "On behalf of the association, vice-president Vinasithambi Nagendram, secretary Paramanathar Thavaraja and member of the executive council Kandasamy Balakrishnan were present on the occasion.",
        "Ten two-wheelers were also received by Deputy Superintendents Bhavanandaraja, Yamunananda and the Hospital Welfare Society. It is noted that Dr. Sathyamurthy had earlier made a request to Britannia Karai Welfare Association regarding the above issue."
      ],
